ct-DRAFT) in `e2e/journeys/`-shape tests with manifest entries; (4) ≥40% token reduction per milestone for execute+verify cycles vs trailing-3 baseline (M52, M54, prior); (5) zero 429 errors at parallelism level D3 declared safe + peak parallelism ≥6 concurrent workers; (6) verify-gate wall-clock ≤ ½ trailing-3 median; (7) Red Team GRUDGING PASS — ≥5 broken patches, all caught (preflight-skip-on-error, parallel-substrate-bypasses-capture, verify-gate-falsy-true, branch-guard-typo, contract-staleness-ignored, brief-staleness-ignored); (8) zero regressions on `npm test` (baseline 2262/2262 unit + 1 documented env-bleed). **Out of scope**: rewriting all 55 command files to call the substrate directly (separate ratchet milestone, pending M55 ship); cross-project preflight/brief propagation via `gsd-t update-all` (follow-up); replacing `bin/gsd-t-worker-dispatch.cjs` or `bin/gsd-t-unattended.cjs` with the substrate (those are unattended-mode supervisors, distinct surface). **Charter**: `.gsd-t/charters/m55-charter.md`. **Standing directive**: execute through to COMPLETED autonomously; only stop for destructive action, unrecoverable error after 2 fix attempts + debug-loop exit 4, or measurement criteria failure (recalibrate and continue, do not tag). |\n17\t| M52 | Rigorous User-Journey Coverage + Anti-Drift Test Quality | COMPLETE | 3.23.10 | 2 file-disjoint domains. **D1 m52-d1-journey-coverage-tooling** (5 tasks): `bin/journey-coverage.cjs` listener-detector + `bin/journey-coverage-cli.cjs` (`gsd-t check-coverage`) + `scripts/hooks/pre-commit-journey-coverage` + `bin/gsd-t.js` wiring (`installJourneyCoverageHook`, `--install-journey-hook`) + `journey-coverage-contract.md` (manifest schema + listener catalogue + gap rules + exit codes). **D2 m52-d2-journey-specs-and-fixtures** (5 tasks): 12 inaugural `e2e/journeys/*.spec.ts` + `.gsd-t/journey-manifest.json` + 3 real-data NDJSON fixtures under `e2e/fixtures/journeys/` + `replay-helpers.ts` + Red Team \"Test Pass-Through 