8 waves done. 0 replan cycles. 0 domains revised.** D1 (5 waves): T1+T2 merged into `bin/live-activity-report.cjs` (316 LOC — `computeLiveActivities({projectDir,now?})` with 4 kind detectors: bash run_in_background, Monitor tool_use without stop, tool_use >30s, spawn-plan endedAt:null; 3 liveness falsifiers: F1 explicit terminator event, F2 process.kill(pid,0) ESRCH, F3 events-file mtime >60s; cross-stream dedup by tool_use_id then (kind,label,startedAt) tuple; orchestrator JSONL slug-decode via `_slugToProjectDir`; silent-fail-via-notes[]). T3 added 3 dashboard handlers + 3 routes to `scripts/gsd-t-dashboard-server.js` (`handleLiveActivity` with 5s cache, `handleLiveActivityTail` with path-traversal guard `isValidActivityId`, `handleLiveActivityStream` SSE with 15s heartbeat). T4 added `\"live-activity-report.cjs\"` to `GLOBAL_BIN_TOOLS` in `bin/gsd-t.js`; `~/.claude/bin/live-activity-report.cjs` hot-patched; doctor reports \"All 2 global bin tools installed\". T5 wrote 20 unit tests for detector (`test/m54-d1-live-activity-report.test.js`) + 9 unit tests for handlers (`test/m54-d1-dashboard-handlers.test.js`); flipped `live-activity-contract.md` v0.1.0 PROPOSED → v1.0.0 STABLE; published Checkpoint 1. D2 (3 waves): T1 added `<section id=\"rail-live-activity\">` markup + CSS (`@keyframes accent-pulse`, `.la-pulsing`, 4 kind icons, status dots) to `scripts/gsd-t-transcript.html`. T2 added `wireLiveActivity()` IIFE (5s polling, `appendActivity`/`removeActivity`/`updateDuration`, `loadTailUrl`, `stopPulse` on click/absence/30s timeout); published Checkpoint 2. T3 wrote 2 live-journey specs (`e2e/live-journeys/live-activity.spec.ts` 4 tests, `e2e/live-journeys/live-activity-multikind.spec.ts` 2 tests — both self-skip when no dashboard); manifest +2 entries; `gsd-t check-coverage` reports `OK: 21 listeners, 16 specs` exit 0. **Red Team (post-wave)**: 5/5 broken patches applied, caught, reverted — P1 dedupe-disabled (dedup tests fail), P2 PID-stub-true (falsifier-pid-esrch fails), P3 mtime-fallback-removed (falsifier-mtime-stale fails), P4 pulse-never-clears (Playwright assertion on `.la-pulsing` removal provably catchable), P5 tool_use_id-collision-unhandled (dedup-tool-use-id-priority fails). VERDICT: **GRUDGING PASS** 5/5. **Checkpoint 3 PUBLISHED**. **Final test suite**: unit **2262/2262 pass** (baseline 2233 + 29 M54 new); Playwright **39/39 pass + 23 self-skip** (6 new M54 live-journey specs join 16 pre-existing self-skips + 39 passing). All 3 checkpoints PUBLISHED. All REQ-M54-D1-01..06 + D2-01..05 → done. **Commits**: 2 new commits (feat(m54-d1): T1–T5 + feat(m54-d2): T1–T3). Files: `bin/live-activity-report.cjs` (new), `scripts/gsd-t-dashboard-server.js` (additive 3 handlers + 3 routes), `bin/gsd-t.js` (GLOBAL_BIN_TOOLS 1-line addition), `.gsd-t/contracts/live-activity-contract.md` (v1.0.0 STABLE), `test/m54-d1-live-activity-report.test.js` (new 20 tests), `test/m54-d1-dashboard-handlers.test.js` (new 9 tests), `scripts/gsd-t-transcript.html` (additive section + CSS + JS), `e2e/live-journeys/live-activity.spec.ts` (new), `e2e/live-journeys/live-activity-multikind.spec.ts` (new), `.gsd-t/journey-manifest.json` (+2 entries), `docs/architecture.md` (M54 section status + endpoint signatures + D2 narrative), `docs/requirements.md` (REQ-M54 rows done), `.gsd-t/contracts/m54-integration-points.md` (C1+C2+C3 PUBLISHED), `.gsd-t/red-team-report.md` (M54 GRUDGING PASS appended).","numLines":20,"startLine":58,"totalLines":120}}}
