es: bootstrap library, spawn-gate, commit-time hook. Also land 5 E2E viewer specs.\n- 2026-05-06 13:45: [partitioned] M50 — 2 file-disjoint domains. D1 bootstrap-and-detection (5 tasks); D2 gates-and-specs (10 tasks). Cross-domain checkpoint after D1 lands (both touch bin/gsd-t.js).\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":63,"oldLines":6,"newStart":63,"newLines":7,"lines":[" "," > Prior decision log entries preserved in `.gsd-t/milestones/*/progress.md` — see archive snapshots for pre-M51 history."," ","+- 2026-05-09 17:07 PDT: M55 D2 — `bin/parallel-cli.cjs` (engine: `runParallel({workers, maxConcurrency, failFast?, teeDir?})` returning `{ok, schemaVersion:'1.0.0', wallClockMs, maxConcurrencyApplied, failFast, results[], notes[]}`; results sorted by id ASC; every spawn flows through `bin/gsd-t-token-capture.cjs::captureSpawn` so the token-log Tokens cell renders `—` for CLI workers per canonical pattern; fail-fast SIGTERM → 5s grace → SIGKILL; per-worker `timeoutMs` cancels only that worker; thin CLI `--plan FILE --max-concurrency N --fail-fast --tee-dir DIR --json`) + `bin/parallel-cli-tee.cjs` (NDJSON tee with file-mode + memory-mode 1 MB cap → tmp rotation) + `bin/m55-substrate-proof.cjs` proof CLI + `parallel-cli-contract.md` v1.0.0 STABLE shipped. **Empirical proof (success criterion 2)**: `node bin/m55-substrate-proof.cjs` reports **5.57× speedup** (T_serial=1813.3ms vs T_par=325.6ms across N=6 sleep=250ms workers, parallelism_factor=4.61, threshold ≥3.0× — PASS). Numbers appended to `.gsd-t/metrics/m55-substrate-proof.txt` and structured `.gsd-t/metrics/m55-substrate-proof.json`. 11 new D2 unit tests (happy-3, throttling-cap-2 via observed peak ≤2 marker-files, fail-fast cancels siblings, per-worker-timeout kills only that worker, tee-NDJSON valid, captureSpawn invariant tokens-log-row + JSONL `hasUsage:false`, validation rejects bad opts, determinism sort-by-id, CLI thin layer + missing-flag exit 2, in-memory rotation on >1MB overflow); suite 2432+11 = 2443 (2441