{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017BzYK2y2DsrCGnj2N7BTaV","type":"tool_result","content":"51\t## Step 2: Full Test Audit (Inline)\n52\t\n53\t```bash\n54\tnode scripts/gsd-t-watch-state.js advance --agent-id \"$GSD_T_AGENT_ID\" --parent-id \"${GSD_T_PARENT_AGENT_ID:-null}\" --command gsd-t-verify --step 2 --step-label \"Full Test Audit (Inline)\" 2>/dev/null || true\n55\t```\n56\t\n57\tRun the full test audit directly:\n58\t\n59\t1. Run the full test suite: `npm test` (or project equivalent) — record pass/fail counts\n60\t2. Read all contracts in `.gsd-t/contracts/` — verify each has at least one test validating it\n61\t3. Check acceptance criteria from domain task lists — verify each is tested\n62\t4. Run E2E suite if `playwright.config.*` exists\n63\t5. Report: comprehensive test results with pass/fail counts and coverage gaps\n64\t\n65\tVerification cannot complete if any test fails or critical contract gaps remain.\n66\t\n67\t## Step 2.5: High-Risk Domain Gate (MANDATORY — Categories 2 and 7)\n68\t\n69\t```bash\n70\tnode scripts/gsd-t-watch-state.js advance --agent-id \"$GSD_T_AGENT_ID\" --parent-id \"${GSD_T_PARENT_AGENT_ID:-null}\" --command gsd-t-verify --step 2 --step-label \".5: High-Risk Domain Gate (MANDATORY — Categories 2 and 7)\" 2>/dev/null || true\n71\t```\n72\t\n73\tBefore running standard verification dimensions, check whether this milestone involves any high-risk domain:\n74\t\n75\t**High-risk domains**: audio capture/playback, GPU/WebGPU/WebGL, ML/inference/model loading, background workers, native APIs (camera, bluetooth, filesystem), IPC, WebAssembly, real-time data streams."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d7a22423-cc58-497c-b885-89dea884b91e","uuid":"823eef53-187d-48cc-9eff-4611f6bd29de","timestamp":"2026-05-10T00:10:04.695Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/david/projects/GSD-T/commands/gsd-t-verify.md","content":"## Step 2: Full Test Audit (Inline)\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/gsd-t-watch-state.js advance --agent-id \"$GSD_T_AGENT_ID\" --parent-id \"${GSD_T_PARENT_AGENT_ID:-null}\" --command gsd-t-verify --step 2 --step-label \"Full Test Audit (Inline)\" 2>/dev/null || true\n```\n\nRun the full test audit directly:\n\n1. Run the full test suite: `npm test` (or project equivalent) — record pass/fail counts\n2. Read all contracts in `.gsd-t/contracts/` — verify each has at least one test validating it\n3. Check acceptance criteria from domain task lists — verify each is tested\n4. Run E2E suite if `playwright.config.*` exists\n5. Report: comprehensive test results with pass/fail counts and coverage gaps\n\nVerification cannot complete if any test fails or critical contract gaps remain.\n\n## Step 2.5: High-Risk Domain Gate (MANDATORY — Categories 2 and 7)\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/gsd-t-watch-state.js advance --agent-id \"$GSD_T_AGENT_ID\" --parent-id \"${GSD_T_PARENT_AGENT_ID:-null}\" --command gsd-t-verify --step 2 --step-label \".5: High-Risk Domain Gate (MANDATORY — Categories 2 and 7)\" 2>/dev/null || true\n```\n\nBefore running standard verification dimensions, check whether this milestone involves any high-risk domain:\n\n**High-risk domains**: audio capture/playback, GPU/WebGPU/WebGL, ML/inference/model loading, background workers, native APIs (camera, bluetooth, filesystem), IPC, WebAssembly, real-time data streams.","numLines":25,"startLine":51,"totalLines":468}}}
